high_descs: Turn to face the white counter-top on your right.
Pick up the candle on the left of the tissue box.
Go to the other end of the counter and turn left to face it again.
Put the candle in a drawer.
Turn around and move to the toilet behind you.
Pick up the candle on the back of the toilet.
Turn back to face the counter again.
Put the candle in the same drawer as the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put the candles in the bathroom in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter.
Pick up a candle stick on the counter.
Turn right and go to the end of the counter.
Put the candle stick in the drawer under the counter.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Pick up a candle stick on the toilet.
Turn around and go to the counter.
Put the candle stick in the drawer under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two candle sticks to the drawer under the counter.

high_descs: Turn right towards the green dresser with white top.
Pick up the bottle from the dresser.
Go right towards the bottom, right drawer of the green dresser.
Open the bottom, right drawer and set the bottle inside, shut the drawer.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and go to the bottom, right drawer of the green dresser.
Open the drawer and put the bottle in next to the other and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles in the bottom drawer of a dresser.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, then turn right so that you are facing the leftmost part of the counter.
Pick up the nail polish sitting on the back of the counter, to the left of the tissue box.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the counter, then turn to your left so that you are facing the counter.
Place the nail polish in the bottom drawer, under the counter, all the way to the right.
Turn around and walk to the toilet behind you.
Pick up the nail polish, on the opposite side of the yellow spray bottle, on top of the tank of the toilet.
Turn around and walk back to the right end of the counter.
Place the nail polish in the bottom drawer, at the right end of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of nail polish in the bottom, right, bathroom drawer.
